SELECT [t].[AuthorId], [t].[Biography], [t].[ImageUrl], [t].[Name], [b].[BookId], [b].[AuthorId], [b].[GenreId], [b].[ImageUrl], [b].[Price], [b].[PublicationDate], [b].[Title]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [a].[AuthorId], [a].[Biography], [a].[ImageUrl], [a].[Name]
    FROM [Authors] AS [a]
    WHERE [a].[AuthorId] = @__authorId_0
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN [Books] AS [b] ON [t].[AuthorId] = [b].[AuthorId]
ORDER BY [t].[AuthorId]
